    <item>
      <title>由于印度订单导致 Paytm 大部分业务暂停，Paytm 受到打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/india-orders-paytm-payments-bank-to-stop-conducting-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度监管机构下令数字支付提供商 Paytm 的母公司停止其大部分业务，这对这家备受瞩目的科技先驱造成了沉重打击，该公司多年来一直与监管机构和围绕中国支持的批评进行斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/india-orders-paytm-payments-bank-to-stop-conducting-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 12:57:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港“水下”抵押贷款水平创二十年来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/hong-kong-underwater-mortgage-levels-surge-to-two-decade-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在香港今年预计将成为全球最糟糕的房地产市场之一的情况下，香港的抵押贷款价值已超过房屋价值，飙升至二十年来的高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/hong-kong-underwater-mortgage-levels-surge-to-two-decade-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:57:33 GMT</pubDate>
